SayHello Privacy Policy

Last updated: November 2025

Thank you for using SayHello! Your privacy and data security are very important to us.

1. Information We Collect
SayHello does not collect, store, or share any personally identifiable information.
All translation requests are processed instantly and are not saved.

2. Accessibility Permission
SayHello may request Accessibility Service permission (with your consent) solely to detect and translate on-screen text.
This permission is never used for any other purpose and does not access sensitive data (such as passwords or payment information).

3. Third-Party Services
SayHello integrates AI translation engines including ChatGPT-4, Gemini, and DeepSeek.
These are used only for language processing and do not receive any of your personal data.

4. Data Security
All translation requests are transmitted securely using encryption.
App data is stored locally on your device and can be deleted anytime.

5. Contact Us
